@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kpunhg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.93)))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.82) * (tmp + 0.09 / tmp + 0.00)) - (0.51 * 0.48))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.72 / v1 + 0.69) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.45)) + (0.67 * (v1 + 0.43 * tmp + 0.70)))
    data[tid] = v0
